# Vendored skin content — preserve byte-for-byte. The repo-root
# .gitattributes sets `* text=auto eol=lf` which silently strips CRLF
# from .less files on commit, diverging us from what's on prod's FTP.
# `-text` unsets the text classification; `-eol` unsets the line-ending
# enforcement (without it, `eol=lf` from the parent still implies
# `text=auto` and re-enables normalization).
* -text -eol
